code: public void setParent(Component parent) {     this.parent = parent. }
public void setChildren(List<Component> children) {     this.children = children. }

@Override public Component getObject() throws Exception {     if (this.children != null && this.children.size() > 0) {         for (Component child : children) {             this.parent.addComponent(child).         }     }     return this.parent. }
